I can't believe it's already been 2 years, it feels like the last time I saw my mom was both 50 years ago and the other day at the same time. Waking up randomly and finding out your favorite person in the entire world is no longer with us is truly something so traumatic that no social media post could ever describe in words, and something I'm still trying to process and heal from. I learned that day how short life really is and how everything can be taken away in an instant so I know appreciate life so much more now. Im thankful for all the fun times we had together and I will be having some wine tonight in her honor! Miss you the most Moot 💞
